commitResults.messageBody:
This enables for batch adding of contacts exported from another
HRConnect app.

The commit has 2 new commands, "import" and "import_file".
"import" command shows the file selection dialog while the "import_file"
imports the contacts from the json file with the given file path. It
could be entered by user to import contacts without the dialog.
